Process called "handle_compilation_error_function" that takes error as Dictionary[String, Any] and handler as Dictionary[String, Any] returns Boolean:
    Try:
        Add error to handler["error_categories"]["COMPILATION_ERROR"]
        Set handler["error_count"] to handler["error_count"] plus 1
        Let logged be log_error_function with error as error and handler as handler
        Return true
    Catch error:
